Package: moveMMPP
Title: Fit Continuous-Time Markov Modulated Poisson Process Movement Models to Animal Resight Data
Version: 0.0.0.9033
Date: December 1, 2025
Authors@R: 
    person("Devin", "Johnson", , "devin.johnson@noaa.gov", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Using animal resight data, the package functions allow the user to 
  estimate movement rates and resource selection using a continuous-time Markov chain 
  movement model. 
